### Global Variables
@paymentProcessorDefaultBaseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8001
@rinhaApiBaseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:3000

### Creates a new payment on Rinha API
POST {{rinhaApiBaseUrl}}/payments HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "correlationId": "4a7901b8-7d26-4d9d-aa19-4dc1c7cf60b5",
    "amount": 19.90
}

### Fetches payments summary
GET {{rinhaApiBaseUrl}}/payments-summary HTTP/1.1
# GET {{rinhaApiBaseUrl}}/payments-summary?from=2020-07-10T12:34:56.000Z&to=2020-07-10T12:35:56.000Z HTTP/1.1
# GET {{rinhaApiBaseUrl}}/payments-summary?from=2020-07-10T12:34:56.000Z HTTP/1.1
# GET {{rinhaApiBaseUrl}}/payments-summary?to=2020-07-10T12:35:56.000Z HTTP/1.1

